Long Distance Movers

The Best Long Distance Movers

Liberty Bell Moving and Storage is the premier moving service for your long distance move. We service the entire country with long distance national moves, to and from New England. Even if you’re Moving to Canada – Liberty Bell Moving and storage can get you there. We have the a outstanding record with the Federal Motor Carrier Safety Administration. We provide customized moving plans for your long distance move that includes shipment tracking, disassembly and assembly, packing & unpacking service and connection services for appliances. Our services guarantee a seamless moving experience! We offer a complete moving service including; Packing, Helpers, Storage and More!

We service the entire United States to and from New England!

Please feel free to Call or E-mail us directly to speak with a Branch Manager.
